      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, dissolve your<strong> tomato paste</strong> and <strong>vegetable stock mix</strong> in 200ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[300ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[400ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong> – this is your <strong>tomato stock</strong></p><p>Chop your <strong>chives</strong> finely</p>",
