    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your<strong> Chinese rice wine</strong> to the pan and cook for 30 secs</p><p>Pour in the <strong>tomato stock </strong>and cook for 3-4 min or until the sauce has begun to thicken</p><p>Drain, then add your <strong>king prawns</strong> and cook for 4-5 min further or until cooked through</p><p>Season with a generous pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and <strong>pepper</strong> and remove from the heat</p>",
